{
  "texts": [
    "Each element within this vector ranges from 0 to 3, mapping the spatial coordinates of objects within a three-dimensional space.",
    "With each movement of the objects, the state vector is accordingly updated to reflect the change, by incrementing the current state with the magnitude of the movement.",
    "The initial state is randomly determined.",
    "• Action Space: The action space is delineated as spaces.",
    "MultiDiscrete, comprising two integers ranging from 0 to 7."
  ]
